#

Slow-Roasted Pork with Garlic and Herbs

315 min
$25
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

PaleoGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodSlow Cooked

Description

A succulent and tender pork roast infused with fragrant garlic and herbs, perfect for an easy family dinner.

Ingredients

  • pork shoulder: 4 pounds
  • garlic cloves: 10
  • fresh rosemary: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh thyme: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • salt: 2 teaspoons
  • black pepper: 1 teaspoon
